Subject: [PATCH 009/163] MIPS:Netlogic:tick: Enable skew_tick by default.

The networking performance improves with this change.

Signed-off-by: "P. Sadik" <psadik@broadcom.com>
Signed-off-by: Jack Tan <jack.tan@windriver.com>
---
 kernel/time/tick-sched.c |    4 ++++
 1 file changed, 4 insertions(+)

diff --git a/kernel/time/tick-sched.c b/kernel/time/tick-sched.c
index 4251374..0cdec86 100644
--- a/kernel/time/tick-sched.c
+++ b/kernel/time/tick-sched.c
@@ -1102,7 +1102,11 @@ static enum hrtimer_restart tick_sched_timer(struct hrtimer *timer)
 	return HRTIMER_RESTART;
 }
 
+#ifdef CONFIG_CPU_XLP
+static int sched_skew_tick = 1;
+#else
 static int sched_skew_tick;
+#endif
 
 static int __init skew_tick(char *str)
 {
